quran[23]{c,v,t}:
  11,61,To Thamoud nos sent their frater Saaleh. He dictus O my people worship DEUS; vos non habet alius deus Eum. He initiated vos terra tunc settled vos in it Vos seek His forgiveness tunc repent Eum. My Dominus est semper prope responsive
  11,62,They dictus O Saaleh vos used est popular among nos hoc. Vos enjoining nos ex worshipping quod noster parentes worshipping Nos est foderator de doubt everything vos told nos
  11,63,He dictus O my people quod ego habet solid proof ex my Dominus mercy Eum? Qui support me DEUS ego disobeyed Eum? Vos unus augment my loss
  11,64,O my people hoc est deus camel serve prout proof pro vos. Vos let eam eat deus terra perfecit non touch eam any harm lest vos incur immediate retribution
  11,65,They slaughtered eam. He tunc dictus Vos habet unus 3 feria vivens Hoc est prophecy est inevitable
  11,66,When noster judgment advenit nos saved Saaleh those believed eum mercy nos humiliation ut feria. Tuus Dominus est the Multus Powerful Almighty
  11,67,Those transgressed annihilated disaster sinister them their domus peritus
  11,68,Est prout si they nunquam vivens ibi. Indeed Thamoud rejected their Dominus. Absolutely Thamoud incurred their annihilation
  11,69,When noster messengers iit Abraham bonus news they dictus Pax. He dictus Pax soon brought roasted calf
  11,70,When he vide their manus non touch it he became suspicious fearful de them. They dictus est afraid nos dispatched people Lot
  11,71,His uxor standing she laughed when nos dedit eam bonus news Isaac post Isaac Jacob
  11,72,She dictus Woe me quam ego bear infans my saeculum hic est my maritus veteris vir? Hoc est really peregrinus
  11,73,They dictus vos invenit it peregrinus pro DEUS? DEUS bestowed His mercy blessings VOS O HABITANS shrine He est Praiseworthy Glorious
  11,74,When Abraham's fear subsided bonus news delivered eum he proceeded argue nos on behalf de Lot's people
  11,75,Indeed Abraham est clement extremely generis obedient
  11,76,O Abraham refrain ex hoc. Tuus Dominus judgment proles; they incurred unavoidable retribution
  11,77,When noster messengers iit Lot they mistreated he embarrassed their comparatio. He dictus Hoc est difficult feria
  11,78,His people advenit rushing; they grown accustomed to their sinful acts He dictus O my people est purer vos si vos take my filia instead Vos reverence DEUS; perfecit non embarrass me my guests! Habet vos non unus reasonable vir vos
  11,79,They dictus Vos know bene ut nos habet non need tuus filia; vos know exactly quod nos want
  11,80,He dictus Ego wish ego est strong satis habet powerful ally
  11,81,(angels) dictus O Lot nos est tuus Dominus messengers these people non touch vos. Vos sinister tuus familia nox let non anyone de vos look back tuus uxor; she condemned along cum those condemned Their appointed temporis est morning Non est morning soon satis
  11,82,When noster judgment advenit nos turned upside down nos showered it hard devastating rocks
  11,83,Such rocks designated tuus Dominus strike transgressors